Functionality 
  Navigate between pages using links in header
    - They will also have a hover over feature
  
  Each park page will provide info specific to that park
    - Photos of park, POIs, activities available, need to know info
    - Links to suggested areas and activities
  
  Each park page will display reviews posted by users who have visited that pageâ€™s park
    - This will be done using a GET endpoint and handler function
    - New reviews will be added to the database using a POST endpoint and handler function
  
  Users can leave comments w/o login
    - Comments will require first name, last initial and comment content
